org.codeavengers.common.dto.wrap

Class CategoryWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codeavengers.common.dto.entity.Category
      • org.codeavengers.common.dto.wrap.CategoryWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, DBEntity, Rest

    public class CategoryWrapper
extends Category
implements Rest
    This class wraps the Category database entity. The Rest interface that it implements indicates that this class participates in REST End-point operations. Further the JsonInclude annotation indicates that the generated JSON will not contain any Empty (e.g. List) or Null data. The JsonIdentityInfo is added to prevent against recursive object tree. This class also defines utility methods to convert between the REST-side implementations and the DB-side ones.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    abhishek
    See Also:
    Rest, Category, Serialized Form
